Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
